name: Divine Brand
description:
Animation of the painting "Madonna and Child" by Fra-Filippo Lippi, probably painted between 1450 and 1465. It is based on a gif cropped to 210x505, which I made in 2014. Now re-edited, video-Mp4, 1080x1080px and with the whole scene of the original painting.
I can imagine the kids after drinking too much cola.
